iend. The police showed up later and assigned jealousy as the motive for the brawl. his brother sometimes takes a nap at lunchtime as he has so much work to do that he feels drained. He usually snoozes on the sofa or at his desk by the fireplace when everyone else's eating lunch outside. He once brought his work along to the library where I saw him dozed off at the end. Having a snooze especially by the fire is a marvelous way to recharge your energy though. His sister has just completed her phd at tokyo university and is on the way to becoming a professor. Japan's on the way to becoming the world's strongest economy."},{"pid":"76c0160082c76b8b3e5d74a434b705d850d96880","tid":1560030,"uid":243668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2250a114c6304643c312128145d096b74b5a8323","tid":1560030,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdafc01846ce163e9cd98dc3b10dc576133887a1","tid":1560030,"uid":243668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲，想聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"想聽d咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:54:06.000Z","msg":"分手過程同佢啲反應"},{"pid":"f40d6b38767b067868ca9ef9c5561ab3b887a6f0","tid":1560030,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"而加同女朋友嘅情況係點啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd59307a28c455f18ab6140805d41f1ff4c42488","tid":1560030,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"無挽留佢？"},{"pid":"b816d947616f751cb6da1055a0ba007a0fbd9651","tid":1560030,"uid":262897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8ba6624ca64aa30f884268f770b3a34fc55e1ee","tid":1560030,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊左8年<br />\n經歷過long d<br />\n同居緊<br />\n本來諗住等經濟穩